<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ a wǒ yǒu yī shì qiú nǐ, shǐ wǒ de xīn qū xiàng nǐ de fǎ dù.
 jiào wǒ zhuǎn yǎn bù kàn xū jiǎ, zài nǐ de dào zhōng shēng huó.
 qiú nǐ jiào wǒ suǒ pà de xiū rǔ, yuǎn yuǎn de lí kāi wǒ.
 nǐ bì tīng wǒ zhēn chéng de qí qiú, yīn wǒ xiàn mù xiàn mù nǐ de fǎ dù.</lyrics>
